game.name: Yuna Kitchen Chinese New Year Cake
game.description:
Yuna Kitchen Chinese New Year Cake is an exclusively-designed cooking game meant to provide the unlimited fun and entertainment to the users. In this beautiful free online kitchen game, you will get a chance to help Yuna to prepare delicious homemade cake for Chinese Lunar New Year. Make sure that you follow Yuna indications properly to create the best outcome in the shortest possible time. She trusts on your cooking talent and will also be there to guide you how to go to make this wonderful cake recipe. 

Start this brand new cooking game with visiting a nearest supermarket to buy all the ingredients that you need to prepare this scrumptious cake. Get them to your home and begin making the recipe by following the needful instructions. Take a bowl and mix some eggs, cream and sugar in it. Check if you have mixed up all the ingredients. Follow the recipe step-by-step and show the world that you are an amazing cooking expert. 

New year is a big celebration enjoyed by people all across the world. Like all other people, Chinese also makes a big plan to celebrate this important day. Yuna, a Chinese cooking expert, wants to prepare a mouth-watering cake in order to surprise all her guests, who are going to visit her home on the celebration of new year. Hope this cake will fulfil the tasting buds of all delicious dessert seekers. You are free to try it out in your home after enjoying this cute kitchen game in your favourite browser in a virtual world.
